"I am okay Tigerhawk except for a shot in the shoulder but not enough 
to get a good Maximal down."

Grimlock then looks up at the space ship. He sees a missle coming at 
Tigerhawk and him.

"Tigerhawk lets get a of here! Missle coming!", Grimlock says as he 
jumps out the way.
